{{!--
{
  "layout": "standard",
  "title": "Vibes DIY for Coaches | Build a Team Hub That Runs the Season",
  "description": "Build simple team tools for coaches—scoreboards, playbooks, schedules, rosters, and team updates. No enterprise sports software.",
